The <code><strong>onupdatefound</strong></code> property of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration</code></a> interface is an <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventListener"><code>EventListener</code></a> property called whenever an event of type <code>statechange</code> is fired; it is fired any time the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/installing"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.installing</code></a> property acquires a new service worker.